Interface CompilationProperties

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompilationProfile, ConflictAnalyzer, ExtensionCalculator, FlowTracer, LimitationPrinciple

    public interface CompilationProperties
    Describes property names for compilation statistics. These properties are reported via the Compilation.getProperties() method.
